From f2e63e9ad19abaa18fa796d35b8bcfeec965855d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sasha Levin <sashal@kernel.org>
Date: Mon, 7 Oct 2019 13:26:28 -0700
Subject: net_sched: fix backward compatibility for TCA_KIND

